               <p>OLD COURT.</p>
               <p>SEVENTH DAY. THURSDAY, JUNE 18.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury. - Before Mr. Sergeant Arabin.</p>
               <p>1312. 
               <persName id="t18290611-315-defend2246" type="defendantName">
                  GEORGE 
                  EDWARDS
               <interp inst="t18290611-315-defend2246" type="surname" value="EDWARDS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290611-315-defend2246" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290611-315-defend2246" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290611-315-defend2246" type="age" value="29"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was indicted for <rs id="t18290611-315-off1657" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290611-315-off1657" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18290611-315-off1657" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18290611-315-cd1658" type="crimeDate">4th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290611-315-off1657 t18290611-315-cd1658"></join>, at St. Marylebone, 8 spoons, value 4l.; 2 ladles, value 18s.; 3 forks, value 28s., and 1 pair of sugar-tongs, value 5s., the goods of <rs id="t18290611-315-viclabel1659" type="occupation">Dame</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290611-315-victim2248 t18290611-315-viclabel1659"></join> 
                  
                     
                        <persName id="t18290611-315-victim2248" type="victimName">
